data.description: Come see this gorgeous property located in Avondale subdivision, home is conveniently located near the city. This house features 4 bedrooms, 2.5 baths, and a utility room is located inside which leads to the garage. Family room is perfect for entertaining, convenient half bath on the first floor .This house has new flooring throughout the first level with carpet in the bedrooms and the stairway. Stunning kitchen, 5 burner gas stove! Quick access to all major highways will be a quick commute to work or school. Home is vacant and waiting for You. Bring offers!!
